The paper discusses challenges and guidelines for reproducibility and proper experimental techniques in deep reinforcement learning (RL). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which is the primary focus of the paper. The paper also discusses the application of deep RL in various domains, such as robotics (cs.RO) and computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of AI techniques in deep RL (cs.AI) and the need for standardization in reporting results in system engineering (cs.SY).
